  header
    h1= title
    p Text Editor is a simple JavaScript application that aims to provide accessibility enhancements to the native HTML #[code &lt;textarea&gt;] elements, allowing users to control and manipulate their data in the text editor as they wish.
    hr
  main
    p It contains very sufficient methods to manipulate the existing text selection range data without providing unnecessary features. This keeps the file size small and the learning curve low, so you can fully focus on the results.
